description: Blowfish BBQ is smoking up a succulent selection of Kansas City-style ‘Q with awesomely flavorful vinegar-based sauces. This cool crew is serving juicy and tender ribs, brisket, pulled pork, and drumsticks, to name a few of their delicious dishes. And don’t forget to dig into their delightful sides, including delicious smoked mac ‘n cheese, coleslaw, redskin potatoes, and so much more!You just gotta go to Blowfish BBQ for some of The Burgh’s best eats!
name: Blowfish BBQ
